Achievements.Name: Overclocked
Achievements.Description: Collect your first power-up. You did? Now go and wipe them all out!

Achievements.Name: Inbox (1)
Achievements.Description: Retrieve a dropped message from a fellow ship in the RM fleet. There is one at the end of Level01!

Achievements.Name: Fragmentation
Achievements.Description: Crush 10 boulders in Level04. Feels good, doesn't it... Your lasers are your friend here...

Achievements.Name: Mr. Anderson!
Achievements.Description: Get infected by the IPA virus in Level05. Um, have you updated your anti-virus database?

Achievements.Name: Trip The Light Fantastic
Achievements.Description: Sustain 10 seconds unharmed and without shooting against the boss IPA_IRecon in Level09.

Achievements.Name: Keep Calm and Don't Shoot
Achievements.Description: Pass through the low-energy galaxy in Level10 without shooting a single bolt. Itâ€¦ isâ€¦ soâ€¦ temptingâ€¦

Achievements.Name: Double Delete
Achievements.Description: Pop both shells of the boss Shift_2LR in Level11. The first half is easy, but can you pop the other?

Achievements.Name: Try Catch Finally
Achievements.Description: Make it unharmed through all the fleeing enemies in Level19... and prepare for what's coming next...

Achievements.Name: Red Pill or Blue Pill? Neither
Achievements.Description: Discover the green gate in Level20 [beyond, beyond, beyond] the two red/blue gates.

Achievements.Name: Garbage Collector
Achievements.Description: Wipe out 30 of the small bacterial minions puffed out by IPA_DRecurse spores in Level29!

Achievements.Name: The Bad...
Achievements.Description: Defeat IPA_IRecon: the first incarnation of the virus in Level09. Now you know the true enemy!

Achievements.Name: The Ugly...
Achievements.Description: Defeat IPA_VInterface: the second incarnation of the virus in Level19.

Achievements.Name: ...And The Worst
Achievements.Description: Defeat IPA_IRecurse: the third incarnation of the virus in Level29. This is the final battle!

Achievements.Name: #include "*.*"
Achievements.Description: Discover and collect all Secret Orbs in Hyper Void... and enjoy the level shortcuts!

Achievements.Name: To The Last Kilo-byte
Achievements.Description: Win all 29 levels in Hyper Mode. Be proud, you have seen each and every kilo-byte this game has!
